	class="text-[14px] text-(--text-muted) leading-[1.65] m-0 mb-5 max-w-2xl animate-fade-in"
	style="animation-delay:0.26s"
>
	I'm a tech nerd who's been tinkering with computers since a very young age.
	<br />
	Born in{" "}
	<img
		src="/images/flag-uk.webp"
		alt="UK"
